      • Prescription

        public Prescription(java.lang.String name,
                    java.lang.String strength,
                    java.lang.String route,
                    java.lang.String frequency,
                    java.lang.String quantity,
                    int maxRefills,
                    int refills,
                    java.lang.String notes,
                    java.sql.Date datePrescribed,
                    java.sql.Date dateFilled,
                    java.sql.Date datePickedUp,
                    boolean filled,
                    java.lang.String pharmID,
                    java.lang.String docLicense,
                    java.lang.String patientMedNumber)
        Creates a precription.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the drug.
        strength - Drug's strength.
        route - Route of administration.
        frequency - How often the drug should be taken.
        quantity - Quantity of the drug (pills, bottles, etc.)
        maxRefills - Maximum number of refills.
        refills - Number of refills done.
        notes - Doctor or pharmacist's note.
        datePrescribed - Date the prescription is written.
        dateFilled - Date the prescription is filled.
        datePickedUp - Date the prescription is picked up by patient.
        filled - True of the Rx has been filled, false otherwise.
        pharmID - Branch ID of the intended pharmacy.
        docLicense - License of the prescribing doctor.
        patientMedNumber - Patient's medical number.
